    <section id="account-issues" class="faq-section">
      <h2>Account Issues</h2>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>How do I create an account?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>To create an account on UniBite:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Click on the "Sign Up" button in the top right corner of the website</li>
              <li>Enter your MIU email address (must end with @miuegypt.edu.eg)</li>
              <li>Create a password and fill in your details</li>
              <li>Verify your email address by clicking the link sent to your inbox</li>
              <li>Complete your profile by adding your student/faculty ID and preferences</li>
            </ol>
            <p>You can also sign up using your Google account linked to your MIU email.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>I can't log in to my account</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>If you're having trouble logging in:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Make sure you're using the correct email address (your MIU email)</li>
              <li>Check that you're entering the correct password</li>
              <li>Try resetting your password by clicking "Forgot password?" on the login page</li>
              <li>Ensure your account has been verified by checking your email</li>
              <li>Clear your browser cache and cookies, then try again</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you still can't log in, please contact our support team for assistance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>How do I reset my password?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>To reset your password:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Go to the login page</li>
              <li>Click on "Forgot password?" below the password field</li>
              <li>Enter your MIU email address</li>
              <li>Check your email for a password reset link</li>
              <li>Click the link and follow the instructions to create a new password</li>
            </ol>
            <p>The reset link is valid for 24 hours. If you don't receive the email, check your spam folder or request another reset link.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="ordering-help" class="faq-section">
      <h2>Ordering Help</h2>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>How do I place an order?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Placing an order on UniBite is easy:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Log in to your UniBite account</li>
              <li>Browse restaurants or search for specific items</li>
              <li>Select the items you want to order</li>
              <li>Add items to your cart</li>
              <li>Review your order and proceed to checkout</li>
              <li>Select your payment method</li>
              <li>Confirm your order</li>
            </ol>
            <p>You'll receive a confirmation notification and can track your order status in real-time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>What payment methods are accepted?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>UniBite accepts the following payment methods:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Student Meal Plan</li>
              <li>Campus Cash</li>
              <li>Cash on pickup</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We're working on adding more payment options in the future, including credit/debit cards and mobile payment solutions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>How do I track my order?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>You can track your order in real-time:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Log in to your UniBite account</li>
              <li>Go to "My Orders" in your account dashboard</li>
              <li>Select the order you want to track</li>
              <li>View the current status of your order</li>
            </ol>
            <p>You'll also receive notifications when your order is confirmed, being prepared, and ready for pickup.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>Can I cancel or modify my order?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>You can cancel or modify your order under certain conditions:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Orders can be cancelled within 5 minutes of placement</li>
              <li>Once preparation begins, orders cannot be cancelled</li>
              <li>Contact the restaurant directly for urgent modifications</li>
              <li>Refunds will be processed according to your payment method</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To cancel an order, go to "My Orders" and click "Cancel Order" if the option is available.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="technical-support" class="faq-section">
      <h2>Technical Support</h2>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>The app is not working properly</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>If you're experiencing issues with the app:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Make sure you have the latest version installed</li>
              <li>Try closing and reopening the app</li>
              <li>Check your internet connection</li>
              <li>Clear the app cache in your device settings</li>
              <li>Restart your device</li>
            </ol>
            <p>If the problem persists, please contact our support team with details about the issue and your device information.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>I found a bug in the app</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We appreciate your help in improving UniBite! To report a bug:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Go to your account settings</li>
              <li>Select "Report a Problem"</li>
              <li>Choose "Bug Report" from the options</li>
              <li>Describe the issue in detail, including what you were doing when it occurred</li>
              <li>If possible, include screenshots or screen recordings</li>
              <li>Submit the report</li>
            </ol>
            <p>Our development team will investigate the issue and work on a fix as soon as possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>How do I update the app?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>To update the UniBite app:</p>
            <p><strong>For iOS devices:</strong></p>
            <ol>
              <li>Open the App Store</li>
              <li>Tap on your profile icon in the top right</li>
              <li>Scroll down to see pending updates</li>
              <li>Find UniBite and tap "Update"</li>
            </ol>
            <p><strong>For Android devices:</strong></p>
            <ol>
              <li>Open the Google Play Store</li>
              <li>Tap the menu icon and select "My apps & games"</li>
              <li>Find UniBite in the list and tap "Update"</li>
            </ol>
            <p>You can also enable automatic updates in your device settings to always have the latest version.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>The website is loading slowly</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>If the UniBite website is loading slowly:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Check your internet connection speed</li>
              <li>Try refreshing the page (Ctrl+F5 or Cmd+Shift+R)</li>
              <li>Clear your browser cache and cookies</li>
              <li>Disable browser extensions temporarily</li>
              <li>Try using a different browser</li>
              <li>Check if other websites are loading normally</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If the issue persists, it might be due to high traffic. Please try again in a few minutes or contact support.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>General Questions</h2>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>What is UniBite?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>UniBite is a campus food ordering platform designed specifically for the MIU community. It allows students, faculty, and staff to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Browse and order from campus restaurants and cafeterias</li>
              <li>Pay using their meal plans or campus cash</li>
              <li>Track orders in real-time</li>
              <li>Skip lines by pre-ordering food</li>
              <li>Discover new dining options on campus</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our goal is to make campus dining more convenient and accessible for everyone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>What are the operating hours?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>UniBite operates according to campus restaurant hours:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Monday - Friday:</strong> 7:00 AM - 10:00 PM</li>
              <li><strong>Saturday:</strong> 9:00 AM - 9:00 PM</li>
              <li><strong>Sunday:</strong> 10:00 AM - 8:00 PM</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Individual restaurant hours may vary. Check each restaurant's page for specific operating hours. During exam periods and holidays, hours may be extended or reduced.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span>Is there a minimum order amount?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="accordion-icon">
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Minimum order requirements vary by restaurant:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Most campus cafeterias have no minimum order</li>
              <li>Some specialty restaurants may require a minimum of 20-30 EGP</li>
              <li>Group orders may have different minimums</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The minimum order amount (if any) will be clearly displayed on each restaurant's page before you place your order.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    
